creator: Unity Five Limited
descriptionHtml:
ZatMobile is a powerful mobile application for use by parking enforcement operatives.

ZatMobile allows your operatives to gather parking charge information along with photographs to the ZatPark parking administration system. It will also enable the printing of tickets using selected Zebra printers on site or alternatively, it will send the vehicle data back to ZatPark so that parking notices can be mailed out centrally.

Important: this app will require an active account with the ZatPark parking enforcement system.

For more information about setting up an Account visit our website: http://www.zatpark.com or call us on +44 3333 440 834.

creator: Unity Five Limited
descriptionHtml:
ZatMobile is a powerful mobile application for use by parking enforcement operatives.

ZatMobile allows your operatives to gather parking charge information along with photographs to the ZatPark parking administration system. It will also enable the printing of tickets using selected Zebra printers on site or alternatively, it will send the vehicle data back to ZatPark so that parking notices can be mailed out centrally.

Important: this app will require an active account with the ZatPark parking enforcement system.

For more information about setting up an Account visit our website: http://www.zatpark.com or call us on +44 3333 440 834.
descriptionShort: ZatMobile is a powerful mobile app designed for parking enforcement operatives.
